#4 â€“ It redefines what budgeting and planning can and will be
I gave an example above about how so-called â€˜Big Dataâ€™ will need to become part of budgeting/planning solutions. This is already becoming a hard and fast business requirement as firms are using other data sources to pre-populate or validate planning data.

For example:

